actionConfiguration.body:
create table
  "public"."employee" (
    "id" serial primary key,
    "created_at" timestamp not null default NOW(),
    "name" varchar(255) null,
    "title" VARCHAR(255) null,
    "email_id" varchar(255) null,
    "personal_email_id" varchar(255) null,
    "birthday" varchar(255) null,
    "gender" VARCHAR(16) null,
    "start_date" varchar(255) null,
    "country_code" INT4 null,
    "phone_number" INT8 null,
    "status" VARCHAR(16) null,
    "primary_department" varchar(64) null,
    "secondary_department" varchar(255) null,
    "manager_email" varchar(255) null,
    "employee_id" INT8 null,
    "location_country" varchar(128) null,
    "location_state" varchar(128) null,
    "location_city" varchar(128) null,
    "location_pin_code" varchar(16) null,
    "delivery_address" TEXT null,
    "nationality" varchar(64) null,
    "area_of_expertise" varchar(32) null,
    "horizontal" varchar(32) null,
    "salary_portal" varchar(16) null,
    "onboarding_buddy_email_id" varchar(255) null,
    "photo" TEXT null,
    "notes" TEXT null
  )
